    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp synchronization, while the chassis has been tightened with Bilstein B6 dampers and high-durometer bushings for sharper turn-in. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been retrofitted with a ceramic solution, and the thermal management system has been optimized with a low-temp thermostat and aluminum radiators. The four-piston Monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors ensure fade-resistant deceleration. This is a mechanically sorted specimen that balances raw feedback with Porsche's signature engineering precision.",
